Is written in Heaven!
Monk
.
Thy words are madness, daughter,
And speak a purpose unholythy lips are livid
Thine eyes are wildtempt not the wrath divine!
Pause ere too late!oh be notbe not rash!
Swear not the oathoh swear it not!
Lal
