There is cultivated in the king's garden at Paris, a species of serpentine
aloes without prickles, whose large and beautiful flower exhales a strong odour
of the vanilla, during the time of its expansion, which is very short. It does
not blow till towards the month of Julyyou then perceive it gradually open
its petalsexpand themfade and die.
